welcome guys. Phavonic, good question lol but hard to answer. If you downloaded all I have posted then you'll have around 30% of what I have on my HD.

80zforever, you are amazing thank you!! I'm jumping with joy right now and it's all thanks to you.  Thank you so much for filling my request so quickly - you have made my millennium!!  You do awesome work and I really appreciate all your wonderful music.  Happy Holidays!!

Hey 80zforever - a big thanks for such a quick upload of The Little Heroes. That's awesome. 

Thanks too for pointing me to that Venetians album. I'd looked through what I thought was all your earlier selections of albums but obviously must have missed that one. You've posted so many by now that you almost need to post a document listing everything so that it's easy to search and find which collection particular albums are located in.

Anyway, thanks again and keep up the great work.
